oup consisting of various high-profile extreme metal musicians. Their debut album Cognitive was released on February 15, 2012.\n\nOn May 28, 2010, the formation of Soen was announced, its lineup consisting of former Opeth drummer Martin Lopez, ex-Death, Testament and Sadus bassist Steve DiGiorgio, Willowtree vocalist Joel Ekelöf and guitarist Kim Platbarzdis. The group\'s first song, \"Fraccions\", was released on the band\'s official website on October 2010. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Soen\">Read more on Last.fm</a>','205109','10845988'),('Morbid Angel','metal',2022,'Deicide, Immolation, Suffocation','Morbid Angel is a death metal band assembled in Tampa, Florida, United States in 1983. They, along with bands like Death, Obituary and Deicide, were crucial in the development of the death metal genre and its standards. Since the band\'s formation, the band\'s leader has been guitarist Trey Azagthoth. The band released their first four albums with David Vincent on vocals/bass and Pete Sandoval on drums, before Vincent was replaced by Steve Tucker for the three following albums. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Morbid+Angel\">Read more on Last.fm</a>','460593','23551070'),('Rainbow Dash','metal',2023,'Sunset Shimmer, Diamond Tiara, Gloriosa Daisy','Rainbow Dash is a pegasus with a blue body and a rainbow lightning bolt cutie mark. She was born and raised in Cloudsdale alongside her childhood best friend Fluttershy and is now based in Ponyville where she maintains the weather in the sky. Rainbow Dash loves flying and is courageous, competitive, loyal, confident, and bold. She is one of, if not the best flier in all of Equestria, according to Princess Celestia. She has a pet tortoise named Tank and is the element of loyalty. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Rainbow+Dash\">Read more on Last.fm</a>','37108','366636'),('Chimaira','metal',2020,'DevilDriver, Machine Head, Bleed the Sky','Chimaira (pronounced /kaɪˈmɪərə/) is an American metal band from Cleveland